### How to install WeeChat via Docker
docker run -it --name weechat weechat/weechat
docker start -i weechat

### netcat
nc -C <address> <port>

### How to use WeeChat
/server add moniker address/port -tls=off -password=pw
/server addreplace ......

/set irc.server.moniker.nicks new_nick

/mouse enable
/close                                              - alias to /buffer close

resources:
https://modern.ircdocs.horse/
git fame (after: pip install git-fame)


